""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
" inside caps
onoremap ic :<C-U>:call HighlightCapsTextObject()<CR>
" to caps
onoremap c :<C-U>execute "norm! /\\u\rv`'"<CR>
onoremap C :<C-U>execute "norm! ?\\u\rv`'"<CR>
